desc: Providing Indigenous plants to the Bellarine Peninsula from the casual home gardener to revegetation specialist. I am committed to growing quality plants of local provenance from seed sourced in and around the Peninsula to preserve our Local flora and fauna for decades to come.

layout.text: Plants Indigenous to the Bellarine Peninsula
Revegetating your property or adding to your home garden? Indigenous plants are a great, low maintenance option that strengthens the Peninsulas biodiversity and wildlife.
